name: Newrelic-safari-extension
body:
Setup Instructions

1. Log in to your New Relic dashboard and click on the application you want to setup.
2. Extract the application and account ID's from the URL: https://rpm.newrelic.com/accounts/<accountID>/applications/<appId>
3. API key can be found at: Account Settings > Api + Web Integration > API Access
4. Enter your credentials and hit Save.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
